>{{citeweb|url=http://haydenclement.com/audio-with-video.html|publisher=Hayden Clement|title=Music and Sound for Picture}}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Award !! Category !! Nominee !! Result\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|2007 || [[Golden Schmoes Award]] || Best Director of the Year || rowspan=\"4\"|''[[300 (film)|300]]'' || {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Hollywood Film Awards|Hollywood Film Award]] || Hollywood Movie of the Year || {{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|2008 || rowspan=\"2\"|[[Saturn Award]] || [[Saturn Award for Best Director|Best Director]] || {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Saturn Award for Best Writing|Best Writing]]<br /><small>Shared with Michael B. Gordon & [[Kurt Johnstad]]</small> || {{nom}}\n|-\n| 2009 || [[National Association of Theatre Owners|ShoWest Award]] || Director of the Year || rowspan=\"3\" |''[[Watchmen (film)|Watchmen]]''|| {{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"|2010 || [[Saturn Award]] || Best Director || {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[SFX (magazine)|SFX Award]] || Best Director || {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[St. Louis Gateway Film Critics Association|St. Louis Film Critics Association Award]] || Best Animated Feature Film || ''[[Legend of the Guardians: The Owls of Ga'Hoole]]'' || {{nom}}\n|-\n| 2013 || [[Hollywood Film Awards|Hollywood Film Award]] || Hollywood Movie of the Year || rowspan=\"2\"|''[[Man of Steel (film)|Man of Steel]]'' || {{nom}}\n|-\n| 2014 || [[Jupiter Award (film award)|Jupiter Award]] || Best International Film || {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"|2017 || [[37th Golden Raspberry Awards|Golden Raspberry Award]] || [[Golden Raspberry Award for Worst Director|Worst Director]] || rowspan=\"2\"|''[[Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice]]'' || {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Jupiter Award (film award)|Jupiter Award]] || Best International Film || {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Satellite Awards]] || [[Satellite Award for Best Adapted Screenplay|Best Adapted Screenplay]]<br /><small>Shared with [[Allan Heinberg]] & [[Jason Fuchs]]</small> || rowspan=\"4\"| ''[[Wonder Woman (2017 film)|Wonder Woman]]'' 