 Velvet]]'s first tour Red Room at Olympic Hall, sold out (8,202 tickets) in 0.8 seconds.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://kbizoom.com/top-5-groups-getting-their-fans-to-struggle-to-buy-concert-tickets-as-they-sell-out-too-fast|title=Top 5 groups getting their fans to struggle to buy concert tickets as they sell out too fast!}}</ref>\n* 2014 Concert (SK) \u2013 The South Korean-Chinese boy group [[Exo (band)|Exo]] sold out 42,000 seats on the group's first concert tour: [[Exo from Exoplanet 1 \u2013 The Lost Planet]] in Seoul within 1.47 seconds through online market, GMarket.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://m.mediapen.com/news/view/28415|title=\uc5d1\uc18c \ucf58\uc11c\ud2b8 \ud2f0\ucf13, \uc608\ub9e4 \uc624\ud508\uacfc \ub3d9\uc2dc\uc5d0 \ub9e4\uc9c4\u2026'\uc5ed\uc2dc \ub300\uc138\ub3cc'|date=April 17, 2014|website=\ubbf8\ub514\uc5b4\ud39c|language=ko|access-date=March 24, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.soompi.com/article/599029wpp/tickets-for-exos-first-seoul-concert-sold-out-in-less-than-2-seconds|title=Tickets for EXO's First Seoul Concert Sold Out in Less Than 2 Seconds|date=April 17, 2014|website=Soompi|language=en|access-date=March 24, 2019}}</ref>\n*2013 Show (UK) \u2013 The return of [[Monty Python]]'s ''[[Monty Python's Flying Circus|Flying Circus]]'' at London's O2 Arena, sold out (14,500 tickets) in 43.5 seconds.<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/comedy/comedy-news/10473279/Monty-Python-reunion-sells-out-despite-extra-dates.html |location=London |work=The Daily Telegraph |first=Hayley |last=Dixon |title=Monty Python reunion sells out despite extra dates |date=November 26, 2013}}</ref>\n* 2019 Tour (JP) \u2013 The South Korean girl group [[Twice (group)|Twice]] Sold 210,000 tickets within 1 minute.<ref>Fastest selling Japanese dometour by a foreign group |url=https://channels.vlive.tv/BF37FF/celeb/1.10345087</ref>\n* 2018 Concert (China)  \u2013 Chinese singer [[Hua Chenyu]] at [[Beijing National Stadium]] sold out (90,000 seats)