ticles/2015-08-17/india-s-indigo-confirms-order-to-buy-250-airbus-a320-neo-planes-idfkj8wd |title=IndiGo Confirms $27 Billion Order to Buy 250 Airbus Planes|work=Bloomberg.com |date=August 17, 2015 |access-date=November 6, 2016}}</ref>\n* 2012 Perfume \u2013 ''[[Lady Gaga Fame]]'' by [[Lady Gaga]] was the fastest selling perfume after [[Coco Chanel]].<ref>[http://tribune.com.pk/story/484269/have-you-heard-everyone-is-going-gaga-over-gagas-perfume/ Have you heard?: Everyone is going gaga over Gaga\u2019s perfume \u2013 The Express Tribune]. Tribune.com.pk (December 25, 2012). Retrieved on June 1, 2014.</ref>\n* 2011 Jetliner Family \u2013 ''[[Boeing 737 MAX]]'' sold over 900 airplanes from 13 customers during launch with the real market value of the order is estimated at about $10.5&nbsp;billion.<ref name=Boe_SW_Firm_Order>{{cite web |last=Bader |first=Tim |title=Boeing 737 MAX Logs First Firm Order from Launch Customer Southwest Airlines |url=http://boeing.mediaroom.com/index.php?s=43&item=2072 |publisher=[[Boeing]] |date=December 13, 2011 |accessdate=December 26, 2011}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.seattletimes.com/business/southwests-order-gives-huge-boost-to-boeings-737-max-program/ |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20160512071008/http://www.seattletimes.com/business/southwests-order-gives-huge-boost-to-boeings-737-max-program/ |title=Southwest's order gives huge boost to Boeing's 737 MAX program|first=Dominic |last=Gates |date= December 14, 2011|archivedate= May 12, 2016|work=[[The Seattle Times]]|accessdate= January 5, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n{{portalbar|Lists}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Fastest selling products}}\n[[Category:Lists of products]]\n[[Category:Records by subject]]\n[[Category:Retailing-related lists]]\n[[Category:Sales]]\n[[Category:Economy-related lists of superlatives|Fastest-selling products]]\n", "name_user": "Kyungsooprint", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eConcerts:Added the number 